### Server Source Code

#### [NEW] [prisma.ts](file:///Users/taranjain/Downloads/Real_Time_Chat_App-main%202/Real_Time_Chat_App-main/server/src/prisma.ts)
- Singleton PrismaClient instance

#### [NEW] [auth.ts](file:///Users/taranjain/Downloads/Real_Time_Chat_App-main%202/Real_Time_Chat_App-main/server/src/auth.ts)
- `hashPassword(password)` / `verifyPassword(password, hash)` using bcryptjs
- `generateToken(userId, username)` / `verifyToken(token)` using JWT
- JWT secret from env var `JWT_SECRET`

#### [NEW] [routes.ts](file:///Users/taranjain/Downloads/Real_Time_Chat_App-main%202/Real_Time_Chat_App-main/server/src/routes.ts)
Express router with these endpoints:

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/signup` | Create user account |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login, return JWT |
| GET | `/api/rooms` | List user's rooms (auth required) |
| POST | `/api/rooms` | Create a room |
| POST | `/api/rooms/join` | Join room by ID |
| GET | `/api/rooms/:id/messages` | Paginated chat history |
| POST | `/api/dm` | Get or create DM room with another user |
| GET | `/api/friends` | List friends |
| POST | `/api/friends/request` | Send friend request |
| PUT | `/api/friends/:id/accept` | Accept friend request |
| DELETE | `/api/friends/:id` | Reject/remove friend |
| GET | `/api/calls` | List call history |

#### [MODIFY] [types.ts](file:///Users/taranjain/Downloads/Real_Time_Chat_App-main%202/Real_Time_Chat_App-main/server/src/types.ts)
- Add `RoomMessage`, `JoinRoom`, `LeaveRoom`, `DmMessage` message types
- Add room-related payload types

#### [MODIFY] [index.ts](file:///Users/taranjain/Downloads/Real_Time_Chat_App-main%202/Real_Time_Chat_App-main/server/src/index.ts)
- Mount Express app on same port (HTTP + WS share port using `server.listen`)
- Authenticate WebSocket connections via JWT token in URL query param
- Handle room-scoped messages: publish to `room:{roomId}` Redis channel
- Handle DM messages: publish to `dm:{roomId}` Redis channel
- Save messages to PostgreSQL via Prisma
- On video call start/end, create CallLog entries

#### [MODIFY] [redis.ts](file:///Users/taranjain/Downloads/Real_Time_Chat_App-main%202/Real_Time_Chat_App-main/server/src/redis.ts)
- Dynamic room channel subscription/unsubscription
- Add helpers: `subscribeToRoom(roomId)`, `unsubscribeFromRoom(roomId)`

#### [MODIFY] [signaling.ts](file:///Users/taranjain/Downloads/Real_Time_Chat_App-main%202/Real_Time_Chat_App-main/server/src/signaling.ts)
- Log call events to `CallLog` table via Prisma

